Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, there's your pen, and we'll be all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put this someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for beating off children and small dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a difference between energy and consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is a realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And within the realm, the realm is dominated by the energy of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's electricity, and then there's the energy of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to say it's electric, you're qualifying the field, identifying the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and then energy is a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:00:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,May I hold your hand for a short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to explain consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I should take some time and go into greater detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In your new book, you talked about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,about fear, overcoming anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just hoping if you could elaborate on the process of deeply surrendering the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting go, resisting it, constantly letting go, resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,People are afraid of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear is just an emotion, and what you do is you let go, being afraid of fear, and you let yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you let fear swamp you, you get swamped by fear, and if you keep letting go, resisting fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes intense, and then suddenly you realize that it's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it's always the fear of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you let go of your fear of death, the fear dissolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say all fear is innately fear of death, and therefore letting go of the fear of death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You experience it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You experience it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You let the fear come up, quit resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you get rid of pain as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go of resisting it, you let go of resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually it just... you disappear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Werner used to call it a stack, Werner Ehrhardt, called it a stack, let go, resisting the stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And the stack is built up over lifetimes, all the suppressed emotional energy that you didn't experience out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems very loud, like it's coming out of the table, but that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems mystical.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was God talking to me at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my name's Ali and I have problems with my liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have problems with my liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have hepatitis C and it's halfway to sclerosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's halfway to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To sclerosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if I can just get some healing from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,healing what's unique about hepatitis C why isn't it a beer a or B what's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:04:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,hepatitis C huh how do you know you got it how you say you got hepatitis C
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,where'd you find that out oh and where does that come from what is it a virus
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and how do you catch this virus all right so what is the treatment for it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,there's there's only one treatment that the Western world has and it's it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a year-long treatment it's basically like cancer treatment what is called
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,radiation radiation it's like that it's like chemotherapy oh it's so it's amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:05:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only like a 50% yeah so you know where you don't have any choice about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the matter huh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,oh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The treatment was worse than the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you pray to God for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a healing, and the karmic propensities
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,will determine the outcome anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here. Wait till I finish this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only do three things at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, we pray for your healing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of this thy servant, this thy child,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,seated before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking for your healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to your karmic balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get this settled down here sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, we'll find out its secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of all these questions asking men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I read your books, and you answered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for just for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha. That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want me to sign any?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the wrong page.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign it right there. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you got usefulness out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's meant to be informative,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and the information itself then becomes inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...just by reading it, and just by being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My eye is shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will sign the back side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll have to go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What book is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks familiar, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Zen of Wang Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Wang Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute you as a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk often of the greetings that the pets give us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,at the very high levels, 400, low levels of 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And can we become that skillful
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to greet one another at that level?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And would there be a way of doing it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as soldiers salute one another, or a child comes into the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get the first part of his question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it in our, the, can we ever become as high as, say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the cat's purr, the dogging,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,where we can greet each other at that calibration?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible for...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As high as what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But the cat's purr is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the cat's purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the cat's purr is at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the cat's purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it ever be possible for us to greet one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We do, routinely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In a spiritual group like this, people hug each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,people love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They sort of bond for long periods of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They see each other at other meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're as high as the dogs are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I sometimes wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Some members of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Some members.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some members.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we said the majority of mankind calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And a dog's wagging tail is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And a kitty's purr is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The majority of people on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,do not have the lovingness or kindness of a dog or a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they kill each other in the name of whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat won't kill you in the name of chief dog, dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over and cut your juggler in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Much less slowly saw your head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, dogs and cats are more benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even mountain lions are benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we calibrate that mountain lion behind the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a mountain lion walk by the house not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking out the window and here's the mountain lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum-ba-dee-bum-ba-dee-bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure what is all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we calibrated that mountain lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After a second near-death experience in 1995,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I began to have satoris,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,where I became acutely aware of the one being of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The one being of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,These can last minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,hours, days, and sometimes weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks seems to be my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Though at the time it seems to be a permanent change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about maintaining a balanced energy level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,After about two weeks, I begin to become overloaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any suggestions on releasing or coping with high energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to release it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean release it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems to build up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It builds up in the body, and the body becomes anxious and overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I, what I do is I go to my psychiatrist and I terminate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he terminate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With a mallet or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You do whatever common sense and intelligence would tell you to do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do the rational, sensible thing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's the, the labyrinth right here, picture of the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,May I hold your hand for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's some medication that relieves this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a curable condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it to be a curable condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You go through periods where you let go of everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,experience the self more strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. But you have to have your knuckles wrapped in order to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However it comes about, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,However it comes about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Harkins, thank you, I have no questions, just thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask for your blessing and a chance for a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to bless this young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I bless you in the name of the infinite love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of the God, Almighty God, our creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:13:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have a picture with you and Susan if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a good one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put your head on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your head on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I want to say thank you, both of you, for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is that sometimes it seems to me that people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,on a spiritual path get almost effervescent and enthusiastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,almost in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I find, for me, my experience is that I get quieter and simpler and I have less and less to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can help me understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to know if I'm missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, everyone is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone experiences it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, the levels that the people reach are not always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And they also have different karmic propensities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And certain states.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they are magnificent, they cannot be really tolerated for great lengths of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy has a limitation, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember finally letting go of ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after ecstasy came a profound peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing more to seek, nothing more to gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There were no other spiritual exercises necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was complete and total.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we talk about stages, you know, we're using generalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're using generalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can calibrate the levels of the various states.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And that sometimes gives you an idea of where you are, you know, on the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let God worry about it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,People try to define it and calibrate it instead of just doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not inclined to calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inclined to just see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, I surrender everything to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now how much do I calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, those are pretty looking things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both again very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just science.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just science?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our sense thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You surrender all things to God as they arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, what do you do when you feel you need to make a decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And been praying on it for quite some time and asking for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and no answer seems to be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they come in skywriting or a voice out of the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How many possibilities are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only two, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean either yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if I don't feel I'm getting either yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Spaghetti or goulash for dinner isn't really important, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I touch your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be enlightened by next Wednesday at noon, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I touch your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,People worry too much about such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always worrying, where am I, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a vanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I beautiful today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror, mirror on the wall, tell me, am I the finest, greatest of them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best when you're worrying about calibrated levels of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to just try and get the general range, you know, get the general range.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're over 400, it doesn't make any difference whether you're 422 or 427 or 418.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're generally in the 400s or if you're in the 500s,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which really I want to know is the general range of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a natural curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming, being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:19:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fixated more or less on the inner, innocent inner child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I run on emotions, right and wrong, and I would like to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling is not good of making somebody, making myself right or making somebody wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right and wrong, that's not, yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And also.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That you mean judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That also.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what right and wrong is all about, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know when my inner, innocent inner child,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because I know immediately that I'm doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't label it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you either have to have apple pie or pumpkin pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it amounts to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in calibrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pumpkin pie and a calibrating apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At one time, one thing will be more attractive and more important than at other times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not only the item itself, but the context in which it's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing about the spiritual pathway, I'll tell you one thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing about the spiritual pathway is that you're on the spiritual pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only thing that's important about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all that's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That you're, you're oriented this way to the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And as the wind comes around like a windmill, you'll turn with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So the speed of the windmill is not what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're turned to the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a windmill at home and sometimes it spins fast, sometimes it spins slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When it spins fast, it doesn't mean it's a better windmill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So your orientation is what you want to stay oriented to the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And so spiritual impetus and suggestions and occasions,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like open, open to them, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:23:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, it's a good thing Marco Polo didn't ask, how many miles have I got to go yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say thank you for the work you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you, Susan, for just being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.55,0:23:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just want you to bless me and my country, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,South Africa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one of them that are from South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to bless him and his country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been studying our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We have quite a few people in South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.45,0:23:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to do as he asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to do as he asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just bless me and my country, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless him and his country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.51,0:23:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless you and your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.83,0:23:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
