Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.08,0:24:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.08,0:24:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought you were taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.55,0:24:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm recurring from the shock of elders, not taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.55,0:25:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would be taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.96,0:25:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am glad to announce I've been re-elected president of the Octogenarian Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.03,0:25:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Octogenarian?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.56,0:25:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question, but I would just like to touch your hand if I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.56,0:25:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.56,0:25:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And have a photo taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.56,0:25:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.56,0:25:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And have a photo taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.56,0:25:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And just say thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.56,0:25:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.56,0:25:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the least, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.56,0:25:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.56,0:25:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.98,0:25:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about the Octogenarian Society is you don't have to be elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.98,0:25:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no meetings and there's no dues or fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.00,0:25:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.28,0:25:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.39,0:25:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.39,0:25:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.39,0:25:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.44,0:26:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote my question down on a piece of paper because I thought I'd forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.10,0:26:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.10,0:26:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For the past three years, I've been having trouble finding consistent work, and yet
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.10,0:26:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.10,0:26:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.10,0:26:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.10,0:26:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Consistent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.10,0:26:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Consistent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.10,0:26:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Consistent work, and yet at the same time trying to evolve spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.10,0:26:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe my parents want me to get out and support myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.14,0:26:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.77,0:26:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Brooklyn, New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.77,0:26:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Brooklyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.77,0:26:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.77,0:26:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.77,0:26:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed to stay home with your parents in Brooklyn beyond a certain age.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.77,0:26:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.77,0:26:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.77,0:26:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned 25 today, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.77,0:26:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're how old?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.77,0:26:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.77,0:26:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.77,0:26:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.77,0:26:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be an embarrassment to your parents that you're still living with your
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.77,0:26:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.77,0:26:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.77,0:26:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to say, is your son still living with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.77,0:26:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.31,0:26:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been having a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.31,0:26:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me some advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.31,0:26:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hard time to find excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.31,0:26:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make up excuses for this idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.31,0:26:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You got things cushy at home, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.31,0:26:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.31,0:26:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it all.
