Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.56,0:28:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. And asking what is the work later, you know, shoveling poo-poo. Thank you for the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.17,0:28:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunity. Yes. I've been thinking a lot about keeping holy company, and you just said that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.75,0:28:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we're as high as it goes here, this group, and I haven't been to a lecture in a while, and I am
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.36,0:28:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,very taken back by the kindness and generosity of the people here. And my question is, I keep
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.24,0:28:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking about a beautiful place, a retreat maybe, where people can go for a week or a month
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.75,0:28:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and study. Maybe there's people there that are mentors. Yes. I guess my question is, how can I be
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.11,0:28:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a part of establishing such a place, a retreat, a study? You would have to find people with a common
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.57,0:29:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,interest. Any monastery would be able to give you at least some connections. You know, there's
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.20,0:29:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,retreats. There's retreats. There's retreats. There's retreats. There's retreats. There's retreats.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.57,0:29:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's retreats. There's retreats. There's retreats. There's retreats. There's retreats. There's retreats.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.59,0:29:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's retreats. There's retreats. There's Jewish retreats. You know, great houses of all denominations, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.29,0:29:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Roman Catholic and Buddha's. I was thinking about this group in particular. Yes, it's the thought
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.14,0:29:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that is recurrent. It's really needs somebody with organizational skills for some financial
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.00,0:29:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,capital to get it going. Shake your hand and take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.42,0:30:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed. Mm hmm. Thank you. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.39,0:30:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,blocks from receiving in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.00,0:30:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.76,0:30:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Blocks from receiving in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.89,0:30:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I go inside, it seems there's some beliefs of being unworthy and not deserving.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.51,0:30:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.90,0:30:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to get past them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.41,0:30:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.73,0:30:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're unwilling to receive, then you're not deserving, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.84,0:30:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it feels unconscious, like I'm not even aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.21,0:30:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels unconscious, the beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.81,0:30:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.07,0:30:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.64,0:30:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's unconscious, you wouldn't be aware that that's operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.22,0:30:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go inside, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.38,0:30:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconscious means you would have no idea what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.48,0:30:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.25,0:30:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you consciously wonder, what is it you wonder about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.61,0:30:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether she deserves serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.76,0:30:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not deserving or unworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.73,0:31:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.76,0:31:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's misconceiving how events come about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.99,0:31:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes things occur because of your own hard work,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.73,0:31:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,not because you're deserving as a gift from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.30,0:31:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I hold your hand for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.31,0:31:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you get things because you earned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.94,0:31:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You earned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.09,0:31:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.01,0:31:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.48,0:31:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.75,0:31:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So God's gift is that he gives you the opportunity to earn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.52,0:31:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The impetus to earn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.67,0:31:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.18,0:31:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.51,0:32:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about, I feel like I have a difficult time
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.05,0:32:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing myself and accepting myself to be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.33,0:32:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.81,0:32:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like that's a hindrance to knowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.25,0:32:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,moving on to knowing the love of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.57,0:32:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.11,0:32:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So when people are loving towards you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.11,0:32:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you reject them or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.07,0:32:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.90,0:32:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe them?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.96,0:32:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.27,0:32:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, and I kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.88,0:32:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a lot of nonverbal things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.94,0:32:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.18,0:32:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.41,0:32:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.41,0:32:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.17,0:32:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.57,0:32:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nonverbal things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.05,0:32:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.74,0:32:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The way people are with you tells you how you're regarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.57,0:32:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to accept or reject.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.04,0:32:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it also represents, of course, their capacity for lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.08,0:32:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.43,0:32:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.23,0:32:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So if they're unloving towards you, it doesn't mean that you are unlovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.31,0:33:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And it takes a while to sort out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.70,0:33:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your willingness to give love is what determines your capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.76,0:33:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your willingness to give love is what determines your capacity to receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.26,0:33:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.44,0:33:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about being loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.98,0:33:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be loving towards all of life and all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.19,0:33:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Every little toad, every tree, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.31,0:33:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Regard it with dignity and wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.49,0:33:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will bring me to know the love of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.00,0:33:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,God is all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.04,0:33:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you appreciate the beauty of a tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.21,0:33:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the beauty of a flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.14,0:33:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the magnificence of a bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.24,0:33:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see, you witness God,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.36,0:34:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the famous story of the hunter who goes duck hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.28,0:34:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And he shoots down this duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.95,0:34:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The duck comes flying down like this, lands on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.15,0:34:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and then its mate comes down and lays over the duck
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.98,0:34:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and covers its mate with its wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.61,0:34:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,50,000 hunters quit hunting after they witnessed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.53,0:34:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing was said.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.63,0:34:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you get the essence of that which is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.03,0:34:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,50,000 hunters gave up hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.40,0:34:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was, they tried to teach him how to hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.76,0:34:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And he had a doe right in his sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.34,0:34:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And he looked through the sight and he saw this,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.61,0:34:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the magnificence of this beautiful deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.69,0:34:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And he couldn't pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.80,0:34:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, I realized that was not a hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.07,0:35:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you kill something so beautiful and stunning?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.05,0:35:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're hungry and you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.82,0:35:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too much of a leftover macho game.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.38,0:35:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it was macho.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.38,0:35:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the 1920s, during the Depression,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.88,0:35:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd go out and get a deer and bring it home proudly over the fender.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.36,0:35:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it doesn't mean that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.46,0:35:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go to any store and buy venison, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.59,0:35:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the significance and the meaning depends on the context,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.94,0:35:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the cultural context, the time and the setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.82,0:35:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 20s, bringing home a deer was a worthwhile endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.84,0:35:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And nowadays, you can just go to Walmart and they got it right on the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.61,0:35:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be a PR.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.76,0:35:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.92,0:35:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, better to pray to Walmart.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.38,0:36:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I love Walmart.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.51,0:36:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.69,0:36:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.07,0:36:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.00,0:36:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.30,0:36:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you want to help me with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.09,0:36:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you want to add?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.51,0:36:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.71,0:36:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.69,0:36:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.44,0:36:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You call it to my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.50,0:36:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.92,0:36:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I got to deal with the lights and the sound and all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.23,0:36:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.73,0:36:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you share with me the essence of the teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.48,0:36:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,on transcending the duality of existence and non-existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.73,0:36:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's experiential, and then there's conceptual.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.61,0:36:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's experiential, and then there's intellectual,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.73,0:37:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.78,0:37:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer arises of itself by contemplating the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.69,0:37:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer is non-verbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.55,0:37:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There is neither existence nor non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.96,0:37:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all concepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.82,0:37:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is, is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.84,0:37:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mind says, well, if it is, then it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.88,0:37:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mind had said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.09,0:37:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.01,0:37:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What does the mind know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.44,0:37:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.03,0:37:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't even try to answer the question
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.86,0:37:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,if it understood it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.15,0:37:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If the existence had no reality, there
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.38,0:37:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,would be nothing to ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.48,0:37:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It answers itself by contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.21,0:38:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I faced that conundrum, I remember, at age three.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.05,0:38:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was suddenly, stunningly hit by the fact that I exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.76,0:38:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute I realized that I exist, a tremendous fear came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.11,0:38:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I exist, it might have come about that I would not have existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.44,0:38:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So then I thought, which is reality, existence or non-existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.50,0:38:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All this was done with knowingness and not a mental verbalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.65,0:38:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That I am came as a terrible shock, because I came out of non-existence, non-awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.44,0:38:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of existence, into awareness of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.23,0:38:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was like suddenly the Klieg lights were turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.75,0:39:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was blinding and shattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.57,0:39:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are just moments in the evolution of a certain consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.11,0:39:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.55,0:39:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have these two crosses that I bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.98,0:39:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered if you would bless them for my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.53,0:39:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to bless these crosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.53,0:39:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I bless these crosses in thy name, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.71,0:39:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.53,0:39:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I bless these crosses in thy name, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.84,0:39:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.61,0:39:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.15,0:39:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.71,0:40:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, we'll just move right along.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.30,0:40:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Move along as fast as we can move, which is the snail space.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.96,0:40:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.71,0:40:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.80,0:40:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.76,0:40:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.26,0:40:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.28,0:40:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.28,0:40:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.96,0:40:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.78,0:40:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.42,0:40:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.00,0:40:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.00,0:40:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.98,0:40:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anxiety is a fancy name for fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.30,0:40:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.94,0:40:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.96,0:40:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.67,0:40:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.19,0:40:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.11,0:40:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.21,0:40:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anxiety is a label.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.07,0:40:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what it is you experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.84,0:40:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't experience anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.26,0:40:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an abstract concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.44,0:40:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.94,0:40:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an abstract concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.94,0:40:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.94,0:40:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.94,0:40:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.94,0:40:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.01,0:40:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.01,0:41:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.01,0:41:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.01,0:41:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.01,0:41:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.01,0:41:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you let go, resisting the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.01,0:41:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.01,0:41:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fear comes up about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.01,0:41:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.01,0:41:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Committing suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.01,0:41:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.01,0:41:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you commit suicide, then it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.01,0:41:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That cures your fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.01,0:41:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.01,0:41:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to tell myself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.01,0:41:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't count because then you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.01,0:41:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That cures the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.34,0:41:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.34,0:41:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.34,0:41:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're dead, you won't be afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.34,0:41:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I'll be worse off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.96,0:41:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what this thing's...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.26,0:41:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's psychiatrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.26,0:41:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's psychiatrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.26,0:41:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's tranquilizers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.26,0:41:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.26,0:41:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can drink and become a drunk and then join AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.26,0:41:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.26,0:41:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.26,0:41:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to serve the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.26,0:41:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do the will of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.26,0:41:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.26,0:41:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's an abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.42,0:41:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me how I'm going to do the will of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.42,0:41:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me how I should do the will of God right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.28,0:41:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I get up, take my clothes off?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.28,0:41:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what do you want me to do to do the will of God right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.28,0:41:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.28,0:41:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.28,0:41:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.28,0:41:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.28,0:41:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.28,0:41:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.28,0:41:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.28,0:41:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.28,0:41:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.28,0:41:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I get up, take my clothes off?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.28,0:41:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what do you want me to do to do the will of God right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.46,0:42:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance the jig?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.92,0:42:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,People get these spiritual concepts and they turn to some kind of verbalized magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.63,0:42:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking for some kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.88,0:42:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual evolution is a very human experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.88,0:42:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's energized by divinity, but it's a very, very human experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.73,0:42:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.73,0:42:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Susie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.73,0:42:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.73,0:42:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.73,0:42:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's not an abstract thing out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.78,0:42:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.71,0:42:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So just live life where it is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.51,0:42:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Live life where it is, not in some abstract questioning realm, which your mind conjures
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.71,0:42:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.23,0:42:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.98,0:42:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.46,0:42:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.46,0:42:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.46,0:42:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.46,0:43:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.61,0:43:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're nuttier than a fruitcake, turn it over to God and say, God, I'm nuttier than
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.05,0:43:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,a fruitcake.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.05,0:43:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Straighten me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.03,0:43:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go see Doc Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.03,0:43:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.03,0:43:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.07,0:43:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.50,0:43:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.50,0:43:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,People get lost in the abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.50,0:43:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.50,0:43:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The non-linear abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.50,0:43:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.50,0:43:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want a blessing and to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.50,0:43:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.50,0:43:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.50,0:43:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.50,0:43:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.53,0:43:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Joe, touch Doug's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.55,0:43:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.78,0:43:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.78,0:43:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.78,0:43:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.78,0:43:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See, he didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.78,0:43:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.78,0:43:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.48,0:43:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.48,0:43:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was for the other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.94,0:43:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.94,0:43:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.94,0:43:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.32,0:43:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.32,0:43:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.32,0:43:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.32,0:43:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.32,0:43:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.92,0:43:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.92,0:44:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.48,0:44:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you there, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.48,0:44:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.48,0:44:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What that is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.57,0:44:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.57,0:44:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.67,0:44:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.67,0:44:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had moments of awakening and revelation, and I would love to ask for your blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.96,0:44:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and support on living in a more constant state of remembrance of my true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.67,0:44:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.17,0:44:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.11,0:44:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.19,0:44:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask for your blessings and support.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.19,0:44:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.19,0:44:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For me to live in a constant state of remembrance of my true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.19,0:44:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Remembrance won't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.23,0:44:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Remembrance won't do you much good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.71,0:44:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.71,0:44:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't remember the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.71,0:44:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to remember when I was full.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.32,0:44:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat a sandwich and be full.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.96,0:44:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Remembrance of that sandwich isn't going to help you any.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.61,0:45:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's spiritual lingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.61,0:45:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just lingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.61,0:45:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.61,0:45:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could I ask for your blessings for me to be in a constant state of remembrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.61,0:45:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.61,0:45:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.61,0:45:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Live it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.61,0:45:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fancy languaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.61,0:45:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.61,0:45:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.61,0:45:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.76,0:45:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what an oddity it is to say remember, to remember who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.84,0:45:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.48,0:45:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.48,0:45:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even bother being a who.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.69,0:45:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.28,0:45:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.28,0:45:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does the who live?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.01,0:45:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget in that Christmas story.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.01,0:45:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives in a cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.17,0:45:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the who.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.17,0:45:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The who's live in Whoville.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.17,0:45:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They live in Whoville.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.17,0:45:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.17,0:45:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.98,0:45:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The who's live in Whoville.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.01,0:46:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.01,0:46:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.01,0:46:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'd like to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.07,0:46:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,About two and a half years ago, I erupted my Kundalini.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.07,0:46:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And over this past year, I emailed Veritas two times in an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.07,0:46:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you answered that and helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.07,0:46:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm very grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.07,0:46:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.07,0:46:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wrote a poem for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.07,0:46:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.07,0:46:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.07,0:46:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.07,0:46:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or would you like to read it later?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.07,0:46:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we'll read it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.07,0:46:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Read it later?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.07,0:46:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.07,0:46:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.07,0:46:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.07,0:46:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.07,0:46:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.07,0:46:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.07,0:46:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.07,0:46:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.07,0:46:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It might scare the people or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.57,0:46:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kundalini who, they'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.07,0:46:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a thank you poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.53,0:46:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a poem of gratitude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.46,0:46:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.90,0:46:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put it on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.38,0:46:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.38,0:46:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.38,0:46:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.21,0:46:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so many good reading words .
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.21,0:46:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.21,0:46:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.21,0:46:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is you had mentioned numerous times that one should be prepared for the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.84,0:47:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,prepared in the event of advanced sudden jumps in consciousness and I guess the repercussions
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.69,0:47:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of that and I guess in not functioning, not being able to function. How does one prepare
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.15,0:47:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for something like that? Just to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.00,0:47:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no places or people that you… Yeah, just to be aware that it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.21,0:47:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it happens, it's unmistakable, so you won't have any problem realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.88,0:47:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, thank you. It comes unexpected anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.88,0:47:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, thank you. Reading about it as one thing, experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.76,0:47:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it as something completely, totally different. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.63,0:48:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My question, as an analogy, we tune up our cars, we get them realigned. I'm looking
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.44,0:48:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for guidance to be sure we're in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.44,0:48:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure my spiritual track is my car is in alignment, that the best way to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.57,0:48:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm a little bit off, stay out of the lion's den, you know? Am I making sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.46,0:48:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you want to know where you are on the spiritual pathway, the various levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.75,0:48:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,are there that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.75,0:48:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want to avoid the pitfalls that I've heard about, but I'm looking for a best
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.75,0:48:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,way to…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.75,0:48:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To self-check.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.19,0:48:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 10,000 ways to God. You want to know which is the best one?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.19,0:48:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.19,0:48:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that you're on is the best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.19,0:48:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the path is, yeah, it's sad. I just feel out of… I don't want to go way off track.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.23,0:48:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.23,0:49:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to go way off track. Your intention is to evolve spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.63,0:49:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.15,0:49:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a person who's spiritual would worry that they're going off the track spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.34,0:49:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd rather be going off the tracks virtually.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.78,0:49:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being so serious. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.98,0:49:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.98,0:49:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.59,0:49:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.59,0:49:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.59,0:49:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.76,0:49:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.76,0:49:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the biggest laughs I've had in my entire life, Dr. Hawkins, and for being
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.76,0:49:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,my dear teacher. Thank you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.15,0:49:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.55,0:49:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.05,0:49:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.05,0:49:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Buddha water. Can you sign that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.48,0:49:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't sign Buddha water.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.48,0:49:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.48,0:50:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sign Buddha water deepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.21,0:50:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha doesn't want me signing Buddha water.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.59,0:50:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, no Buddha water signing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.36,0:50:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put this down behind the tape with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.73,0:50:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.00,0:50:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, or whatever time it is, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.55,0:50:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.53,0:50:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, I'm an actor in this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.59,0:50:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and my question is, I was wondering if you know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.94,0:50:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of any actors whose work calibrates above 540
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.51,0:50:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that I could study and emulate?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.92,0:50:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't calibrated actors in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.78,0:50:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, could I ask another question?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.30,0:50:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.55,0:50:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember my backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.67,0:51:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My backup, you're supposed to ask one.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.32,0:51:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, so, yeah, okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.21,0:51:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh yes, that's the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.55,0:51:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I got into your work my senior year of college,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.15,0:51:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody in my class kind of thought
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.96,0:51:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd gone off the deep end, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.03,0:51:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.73,0:51:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the last thing I did is I created this one-man show.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.98,0:51:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was based on your life's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.57,0:51:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of got to silence my naysayers,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.61,0:51:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd love to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.32,0:51:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about 18 minutes long.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.98,0:51:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.11,0:51:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's based on your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.96,0:51:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your name on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.88,0:51:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.21,0:51:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.42,0:51:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.36,0:51:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're in the theatrical business?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.59,0:51:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.42,0:51:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.26,0:51:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see you dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.75,0:52:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I love to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.73,0:52:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been a dancer in this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.17,0:52:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.13,0:52:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't afford the frivolity of being a dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.55,0:52:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Had more serious things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.67,0:52:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't follow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.65,0:52:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to gently shake your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.25,0:52:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,look you in the eye, and say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.59,0:52:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.00,0:52:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.34,0:52:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for putting us in speaking time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.26,0:52:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.05,0:52:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come on, let's move it fast, because-
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.23,0:52:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move it, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.36,0:52:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a lot of people who want to ask questions, and-
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.63,0:52:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.30,0:52:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.30,0:52:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.30,0:52:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.30,0:52:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.30,0:52:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, what exactly is the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.40,0:53:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and how is it related to the human brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.38,0:53:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the mind is, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.34,0:53:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain is obviously a series of neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.44,0:53:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One side of the brain is spiritually oriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.78,0:53:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one is ego-oriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.76,0:53:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of knowingness and mind is a nonlinear energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.21,0:53:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and this energy field is what activates the neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.96,0:53:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is actually non-physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.50,0:53:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.26,0:53:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This energy field then energizes the dendrites in the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.26,0:53:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,where it goes from the etheric body to the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.90,0:53:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mechanics of that are very similar to Maxwell's,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.19,0:53:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to Maxwellian physics of magnetism creates electricity
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.67,0:53:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in a wire, or vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.86,0:54:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Electricity in a wire creates magnetism.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.44,0:54:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So electricity and magnetism are fields that can be switched back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.21,0:54:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So the etheric body, this is what all the students of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.15,0:54:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the professors and all can figure out, is how does the etheric body,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.00,0:54:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which is non-physical, activate the physical body, which is physical?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.53,0:54:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they use Maxwell's theorem,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.82,0:54:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they have the obvious answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.13,0:54:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy is in the etheric body,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.07,0:54:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the etheric body activates the neuronal physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.92,0:54:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like, so the brain is the wires,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.96,0:54:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is the electrical field that activates the neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.30,0:54:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer is very simple, although they fool
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.34,0:54:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,around with it decade after decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.48,0:54:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.86,0:54:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.38,0:54:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.82,0:54:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure it out later probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.07,0:54:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.76,0:55:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.32,0:55:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand the relationship between magnetism and electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.44,0:55:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.01,0:55:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.36,0:55:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to take a while to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.51,0:55:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the energy activates the neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.84,0:55:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.30,0:55:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.34,0:55:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're brainless, don't have a brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.15,0:55:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,then the energy field doesn't get transmitted to the human domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.30,0:55:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.19,0:55:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.88,0:55:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.00,0:55:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking this question on behalf of a number of people
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.07,0:55:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,who are using methadone maintenance as a part of their recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.17,0:55:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're using what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.01,0:55:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Methadone maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.36,0:55:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.19,0:55:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question is, can being on methadone maintenance
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.46,0:55:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of itself limit or somehow negatively affect one's level
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.63,0:55:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness, and if so, in what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.90,0:55:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be holding you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.94,0:55:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The methadone serves for a period, but it's only a crutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.28,0:56:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't live forever on methadone, and sooner or later,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.11,0:56:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to face this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.01,0:56:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to withdraw, and you have to face the living it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.46,0:56:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You follow the 12-step program, and you follow it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.26,0:56:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, great numbers of people have gone
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.46,0:56:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from very addicting drugs to less addicting drugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.90,0:56:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to dependency on a 12-step program,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.73,0:56:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually drug-free, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.36,0:56:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So it may hold them back on the level of consciousness until?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.94,0:56:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the dependency on methadone itself has
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.82,0:56:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to be overcome sooner or later, and it's the fear of a relapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.73,0:56:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel like you get dependent on the methadone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.51,0:56:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But what you do is progressively,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.21,0:56:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,very small increments, reduce the methadone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.36,0:56:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.88,0:57:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.26,0:57:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.98,0:57:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you a puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.69,0:57:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.98,0:57:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a special puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.28,0:57:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a third eye here, and then he also has a voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.94,0:57:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's got the tail, and this is a tail wagging.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.90,0:57:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.44,0:57:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that is funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.61,0:57:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.55,0:57:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My .
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.03,0:57:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kelsey will go crazy over that, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.38,0:57:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kelsey will go crazy over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.30,0:57:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kelsey's going to study that thing
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.78,0:57:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for days before she touches it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.98,0:57:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My dog's just going to look at it and, good God,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.50,0:57:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,can't imagine what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.98,0:57:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughing like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.15,0:58:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and our parrot will study its noises, and that's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.46,0:58:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.48,0:58:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.30,0:58:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to a good home.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.21,0:58:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.92,0:58:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.28,0:58:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.53,0:58:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.21,0:58:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins and Susan, and thank you for your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.76,0:58:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because the Albuquerque Hawkins group would have nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.51,0:58:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to talk about if we didn't have your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.80,0:58:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.15,0:58:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here with a question from my minister,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.80,0:58:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,whose wife is in hospice right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.90,0:58:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife is in a hospice.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.46,0:58:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hospice, hospice.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.40,0:58:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been in hospice for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.84,0:58:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so you may get the framing of this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.78,0:59:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can one person somehow take on another person's
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.48,0:59:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,karma as a favor to the devotee?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.63,0:59:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.44,0:59:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypothetically, there's ways that it is said to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.78,0:59:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, myself I'm dubious.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.23,0:59:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a picture with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.23,0:59:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.38,0:59:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot really take on another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.15,0:59:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's karma. Yeah, you cannot really take it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.00,0:59:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really take it on because you owe the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.50,0:59:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you could take part in their karma if they needed help.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.03,0:59:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. It would be part and parcel of the solution, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.17,0:59:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.57,0:59:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.38,0:59:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone leave their book?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.59,1:00:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dropped their book? Oh, the guy with the dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.94,1:00:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy with the dog who left his book.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.78,1:00:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, I would like to thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.90,1:00:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for telling me the truth, the whole truth
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.96,1:00:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing but the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.48,1:00:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for that all my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.21,1:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.96,1:00:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you say more about our guardian angels?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.07,1:00:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The guardian angels?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.13,1:00:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Guardian angels are, you can communicate with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.11,1:01:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They themselves are on this pathway of spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.13,1:01:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and their task is to be available as counsel.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.94,1:01:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.42,1:01:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then someday you'll have a chance to become a guardian angel
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.80,1:01:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or an advisory angel.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.25,1:01:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They have different ranks.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.46,1:01:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they linked with us karmically as individuals?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.07,1:01:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.78,1:01:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're very available.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.96,1:01:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Guardian angels are very available.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.76,1:01:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think when you ask for a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.84,1:01:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, they become activated.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.01,1:01:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're really seeing it as they see it from a higher level.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.78,1:02:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.86,1:02:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when guardian angels lifted my etheric body
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.71,1:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,out of my physical body
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.92,1:02:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when I went through surgery with an anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.61,1:02:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was like lifted.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.88,1:02:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lifted out of the body into a beatific space.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.90,1:02:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The space was so beatific
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.73,1:02:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that I was sad when the surgery was over
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.03,1:02:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had to go back to an ordinary state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.63,1:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.50,1:02:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.21,1:02:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.07,1:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the past few months,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.46,1:02:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've started having spiritual experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.19,1:02:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,where my mind was just clear
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.26,1:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't feel the need to make opinions
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.73,1:02:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,or to think about anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.67,1:02:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.86,1:02:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I was trying to,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.01,1:02:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to think of a question to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.28,1:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only thing that I could come,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.94,1:02:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that I could bring to my mind
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.96,1:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was just that I love you
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.90,1:03:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and I love everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.44,1:03:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I love the Lord so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.82,1:03:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.38,1:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you transcended discursive mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.15,1:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You transcended the discursive mind
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.09,1:03:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and became only the witness mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.38,1:03:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering whether I could receive your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.11,1:03:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.82,1:03:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.01,1:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.11,1:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.67,1:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.73,1:03:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.75,1:03:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.78,1:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.84,1:03:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.86,1:03:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.88,1:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.90,1:03:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.92,1:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.03,1:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.15,1:03:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.23,1:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wish you well on your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.76,1:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.88,1:04:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.09,1:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to sign this?
