Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.88,1:06:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.75,1:06:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.59,1:06:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot for everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.67,1:06:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your work has transformed my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.11,1:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.15,1:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For the better, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.69,1:06:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Much for the better.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.59,1:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.17,1:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Big time.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.17,1:06:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.59,1:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.46,1:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you too, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.36,1:06:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have, your work has taught me the real meaning of unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.82,1:06:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is what I live for.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.13,1:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is what I live by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.13,1:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.84,1:06:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.84,1:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You love the trees.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.84,1:06:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You love the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.84,1:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You love the grass.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.84,1:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.84,1:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.84,1:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I go to school for botany.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.84,1:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I definitely love the plants.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.84,1:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You love all the people in the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.84,1:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You love the bums on the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.84,1:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.84,1:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.84,1:06:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.84,1:06:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.84,1:06:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I sit down and talk with them whenever I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.84,1:06:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.84,1:06:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I just shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.84,1:06:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.84,1:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to ask if maybe I could hold something in mind and you could tell me whether
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.25,1:07:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it's true or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.65,1:07:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just hold it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.65,1:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.65,1:07:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.90,1:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.90,1:07:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get his question.
