Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.23,1:07:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.23,1:07:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What he's holding in mind, I have permission to ask if it's true or false.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.61,1:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.61,1:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What he's holding in mind is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.61,1:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.61,1:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What he's holding in mind is false.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.61,1:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.61,1:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Score.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.05,1:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.05,1:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.05,1:07:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the answer you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.44,1:07:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.44,1:07:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.65,1:07:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
