Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.44,1:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.94,1:07:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.46,1:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I really believe that I see the effects of angels all throughout nature
