Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.46,1:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.46,1:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I really see the artwork that they leave afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.46,1:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.46,1:08:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is God's artwork.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.46,1:08:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The clouds in the sky and the grass, the trees.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.46,1:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
