Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.98,1:11:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the years when I've asked questions I've always had some non-verbal knowing
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.59,1:11:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the years when I've asked questions I've always had some non-verbal knowing
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.64,1:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that's come from the question that's given me the insight and over the years
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.75,1:11:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,hesitate those that have choked on the virtues of life no
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.94,1:11:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,exposed to kinesiology, I've come across a resistance to it that I've worked on for several
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.48,1:11:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,years now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.48,1:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still notice that there's a resistance to doing kinesiology rather than just asking
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.80,1:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.80,1:11:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then don't do it.
