Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.82,1:11:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.82,1:11:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It just seemed like to me that part of what my knowingness showed was that in some cases
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.59,1:11:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be useful, and yet I saw some resistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.85,1:11:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.85,1:12:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It just works for us and other people, but if it doesn't work for you, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.32,1:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It still stands on its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.00,1:12:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a blessing.
