Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.10,1:12:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to give you my blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.10,1:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you have my blessing, and God bless your sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.22,1:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I lack boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.57,1:12:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.09,1:12:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She likes boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.09,1:12:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.09,1:12:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.09,1:12:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't like them?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.09,1:12:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I lack them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.09,1:12:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you like boundaries?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.34,1:12:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.34,1:12:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She lacks boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.34,1:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.34,1:12:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.34,1:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.21,1:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.21,1:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the process of being me, I have no boundaries, and it gets me into trouble in my personal
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.68,1:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,life and in my professional life.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.68,1:12:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any advice?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.68,1:13:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, the boundaries have to do with the child in you refusing to accept adult
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.06,1:13:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.06,1:13:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want to, you know, indulge in being the irresponsible child who has everything
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.22,1:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,its own way, and refusing to become an adult, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.05,1:13:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say within yourself there's the child and the adult and the parent, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.76,1:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes what happens is the child wants to defy the parent, and then they miss being
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.10,1:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,an adult.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.56,1:14:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I work very hard and I give.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.56,1:14:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Work very hard and what?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.56,1:14:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she works very hard and she's very giving, for that, which is their fault
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.47,1:14:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for those lines, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.85,1:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's not the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.31,1:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is you don't recognize boundaries, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.93,1:14:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
