Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.43,1:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,necessarily respect you because you're so compliant and obsequious they
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.22,1:16:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,secretly think you're sort of an idiot
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.77,1:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's the solution don't give everybody your last Kleenex
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.47,1:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,okay right yeah look you have to watch out for yourself so the adult and you
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.50,1:17:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,have to take charge a little bit of the child yeah you can't let the child rule
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.06,1:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,mm-hmm thank you it's great yeah thank you for your cure you could wash the car
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.46,1:17:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,on the way out thank you dr. Hawkins and Susan I I wrote a book called food and
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.90,1:17:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness and I wanted to gift it to you to my friend Steven help me write it
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.28,1:17:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and our friend Lou Marzellus edited it so that's a gift all right thank you and
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.93,1:17:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I signed it oh thank you very much thank you thanks and I my my work is to get
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.28,1:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,more local organic and sustainable food
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.67,1:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,get what local organic sustainable food in the schools and into businesses in
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.31,1:18:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,general what is sustainable mean that means that we're not using chemicals
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.43,1:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,with the animals and we're not confining the animals and that means we're not
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.93,1:18:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,pouring pesticides on the vegetables and the fruit like that you mean organic
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.78,1:18:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,organic yeah okay sustainable means that future generations the planet will still
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.51,1:18:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,be healthy or healthy
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.67,1:18:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you're worried about the planet I thought you were about the kids I am
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.71,1:18:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,worried about the kids well you got your choice kids are planning the kids
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.50,1:18:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah and I'm wondering yeah you have permission to bless that work bless the
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.06,1:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,work that I do your organic foods for children that doesn't need being blessed
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.53,1:19:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,well right now they're not eating it so I'm trying to so I'm trying to get maybe
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.53,1:19:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you're carried away with do-good or
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.81,1:19:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I'm not. I hope I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.02,1:19:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an article in the Arizona Republic about
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.59,1:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,organically growing pork. There's a guy down in
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.02,1:19:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think somewhere in Phoenix that's doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.02,1:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They were saying that the restaurants are just craving for
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.02,1:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a whole network out there that is organically growing food
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.02,1:19:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and these different farmers are bringing it to the restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.02,1:19:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you know anything about that. Not about that, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.02,1:19:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll simplify it and can I have a blessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.15,1:19:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to bless this young man. He looks pure
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.27,1:20:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and organic to me. God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.77,1:20:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.65,1:20:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for chemicals we'd all be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.51,1:20:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I get his intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.60,1:20:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.60,1:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to meet you Dr. Atkins since 2003 and I finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.60,1:20:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You came from the moon or where?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.21,1:20:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm a loony.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.01,1:20:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me that any question I ask you once
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.01,1:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,asked and answered by you will only lead to another question.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.01,1:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So my only question to you is may I hold your hand for about five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.01,1:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.77,1:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.77,1:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.77,1:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.77,1:21:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. This is my first time here and I just want to thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.69,1:21:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for your love, teaching and inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.93,1:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.93,1:21:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me. Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.44,1:21:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Susan. Hi Dr. Atkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.44,1:21:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.44,1:21:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I'm coming from Germany and I just would like to thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.44,1:21:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask for your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.44,1:21:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.53,1:21:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from Germany.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.53,1:21:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,From England?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.53,1:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.53,1:21:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.53,1:21:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I just get your blessings on your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.53,1:21:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we have permission to give him our blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.73,1:21:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.73,1:21:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to give thanks for this gentleman's approach
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.80,1:21:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and his request for thy blessing, O Lord. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.60,1:21:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.32,1:21:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I took 12 years of German.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.64,1:22:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,12.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.64,1:22:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,12 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.44,1:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I love German.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.42,1:22:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was speaking it last week, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.80,1:22:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's translating all of our books into German.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.50,1:22:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.50,1:22:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just getting bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.50,1:22:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grew up, the guys took German and the girls took French.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.85,1:22:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Real guys didn't take French.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.17,1:22:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.17,1:22:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.17,1:22:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you for the many, many gifts I've received through you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.35,1:22:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very, very appreciative.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.86,1:22:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.86,1:22:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.86,1:22:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know if it would be possible to receive a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.86,1:22:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to bless this young man.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.60,1:23:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I bless you in the name of the Lord. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.60,1:23:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.98,1:23:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.72,1:23:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.72,1:23:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.72,1:23:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.72,1:23:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.72,1:23:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.72,1:23:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.02,1:23:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.02,1:23:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.06,1:23:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.60,1:23:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.76,1:23:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.76,1:23:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.76,1:23:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The question I have is for several people.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.76,1:24:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no depth of separation from God that one cannot surrender from?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.01,1:24:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no depth from God that one cannot surrender from?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.73,1:24:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.73,1:24:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's like how low do you go before...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.34,1:24:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.34,1:24:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you completely be separated from God, say, in levels of hell or separateness and not...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.34,1:24:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible to come out very deep levels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.76,1:24:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.76,1:24:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And by appropriate prayer and inner spiritual work, it's possible to come up from pretty low regions of hell out of God's forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.88,1:24:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You pray for forgiveness for your ignorance and willfulness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.31,1:24:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes um hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.40,1:25:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.86,1:25:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With the exception of blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.39,1:25:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.48,1:25:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For blasphemy, there is no forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.48,1:25:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There is this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.57,1:25:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. That's scary.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.93,1:25:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord David, I would like to ask you a question
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.93,1:25:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,about NLP
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.93,1:25:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and how conducive is NLP
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.93,1:25:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or neuro-linguistic programming
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.93,1:25:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in someone's spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.93,1:25:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in someone's spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.93,1:25:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have forgotten what I used to
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.93,1:25:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,about NLP? I really can't answer anymore. I don't remember anybody. It's too many
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.88,1:25:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,years ago, decades ago. I'm saying that because at this point in time I feel
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.77,1:25:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that nothing in this world of form ever satisfied me anymore. Yes. Everything is
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.97,1:26:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,just fleeting and it's like I'm playing a game of meaningless. I know there is
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.63,1:26:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing there besides your work and spirituality and meditation. Yes. And I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.09,1:26:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to, the experiencer, as you put it, tries to juice life a little bit more. So
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.44,1:26:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why. Tries to what? Tries to juice life, to juice life, to have more love and
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.84,1:26:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,compassion and passion and all these great qualities. Oh yes, yes, okay. Do you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.34,1:26:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,listen to beautiful music? Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.19,1:26:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's very important. Every day. Yeah, good. Then you're safely on your way because
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.82,1:26:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the field that you move into. The field of infinite beauty. Yeah. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.26,1:27:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,very much. I appreciate it. Yeah. Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.61,1:27:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Vee-oo or is-this? Do-for-for. Huh? That's what he said. This one? Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.31,1:27:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. When the Buddha taught the mystic law of the Lotus Sutra,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.15,1:27:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what was he referring to? When the Buddha taught what? The mystic law of the Lotus Sutra.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.14,1:27:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to recall the Lotus Sutra. Those are the chants.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.35,1:27:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nam-myoho-renge-kyo. What? Those are the chants. You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.38,1:27:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't recall the Lotus Sutra right now. Okay, thank you. I've read so many
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.38,1:28:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual works by so many spiritual masters that I'm getting too old to remember who wrote what.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.80,1:28:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for both of your work. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.80,1:28:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I calibrated the Lotus Sutra. Let's see. The Lotus Sutra calibrates over 700, 750.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.18,1:28:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Around, I remember it was around 720, over 700. Mm-hmm. Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.56,1:28:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no questions. I just do want to hold your hands with the, with looking to your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.56,1:29:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Thank you. God bless you. Beautiful child of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.28,1:29:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan, I want to find my true vocation. I'm a Korean transcendental medicine doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.65,1:29:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am satisfied with my job at the current, in a certain degree, but I always feel that something is missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.14,1:29:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have the talent to be a doctor? I think I might be…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.14,1:29:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asking a lot of questions. Let's think them apart one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.14,1:29:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the first question?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.19,1:29:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Her true vocation is a transcendental medicine doctor. I don't know what transcendental…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.46,1:30:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's TM. Okay, right now being a TM teacher is sufficient, adequate.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.46,1:30:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a teacher, a TM teacher right now is very, very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.88,1:30:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She also feels that something is missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.88,1:30:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to go higher. She wants to go higher than just TM.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.88,1:30:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,TM is limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.88,1:30:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She says, do I have the talent to become a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.28,1:30:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Medical doctor? We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.71,1:30:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She has the adequate intellectual apparatus or
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.71,1:30:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the overall talents to become a medical doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.71,1:30:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We got that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.11,1:30:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a medical doctor
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.11,1:30:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,would be good.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.36,1:30:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are good as the transcendental
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.36,1:30:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,medical doctor too.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.36,1:31:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you want to go higher. You want to be more successful
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.36,1:31:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and go higher. So we got yes on both answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.36,1:31:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Look happy. Please look happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.64,1:31:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Is there someone that can speak Korean?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.27,1:31:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone here that translates and knows English?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.00,1:31:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is yes and yes. Yes and yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.68,1:31:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.72,1:31:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all of our books in Korean.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.35,1:31:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no question. I just want to hold your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.35,1:31:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.68,1:32:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless. God bless. God bless.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.82,1:32:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.34,1:32:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're going to start the shaking hands now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.73,1:32:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to have to sign some books online
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.73,1:32:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because we didn't get them all signed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.73,1:32:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to say something to end the lecture?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.73,1:32:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we didn't end the lecture. We're just shaking hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.09,1:32:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. We'll do it at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.98,1:33:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We're going to shake everyone's hand that we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.98,1:33:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We try to do that at every lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.98,1:33:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's so many at this lecture today,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.98,1:33:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it may take us a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.98,1:33:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to the back of the theater
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.98,1:33:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and come around so that we don't have a clock up here in the front.
